  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Independent review of the implementation of the Government of Rwanda PFM Reforms</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main objectives of this assignment are to: 

(a) Make a detailed assessment of the performance of the 11 outcomes having 13 indicators for the 7 programmes of the PFM SSP (2013-2018); 

(b) Assess the performance of the PFM SSP starting from FY 2013 focusing on efficiency and effectiveness; 

(c) Identify key lessons and propose practical recommendations and priorities pertinent for the design of the next PFM strategic plan (2018-2023) in line with GoR&#x2019;s medium term and long term ambitions as outlined in the EDPRS III, and Vision 2050. 

(d) Prepare a five year PFM Strategic Plan starting from 2018-2023.</narrative>
  </description>
